<h1>Conditions</h1>
<div class="scroll-box">
  <div class="conditions">
    <div class="deathThrows">
      <b> Death Saving Throw</b>:<br />
      roll a flat d20 no modifier, three rolls above 10 stabilizes, three rolls
      under 10 you die, roll a 1 counts as 2 fails, roll 20 automatically alive
      with 1 hp, damage past 0 that equals your full health auto death, party
      member can administer first aid to stabilize must roll DC 10 or hirer
      Wisdom / Medicine check + modifier, if stabilized you remain at 0 hp and
      stay unconscious but no longer need to roll death saving throws
    </div>
    <div class="food">
      <b> Food </b>:<br />
      Can survive with out food for 3 days + Con Mod, beyond that you become
      "exhausted" food food food
    </div>
    <div class="water">
      <b> Water</b>:<br />
      1 - 2 gallons per day depending on heat, after that must make DC 15 Con
      saving throw, or become increasingly "exhausted" per day with out water
    </div>
    <div class="falling">
      <b>Falling</b>:
      <br />1d6 bludgeoning damager per 10ft max 20d6, lands prone
    </div>
    <div class="suffocating">
      <b>Suffocating</b>:
      <br />can hold breath for 1min + Con mod past that can survive rounds
      equal to con mod before dying flat out
    </div>

    <div class="blinded">
      <b>Blinded</b>
      <br />attacks on creature have advantage, blinded has disadvantage,
      automatically fail ability checks that require sight
    </div>
    <div class="charmed">
      <b>Charmed</b><br />can't target the charmer with attacks, ability's or
      spells, charmer has advantage against charmed person
    </div>
    <div class="deafened">
      <b>Deafened</b><br />fails any check that requires hearing
    </div>
    <div class="frightened">
      <b>Frightened</b><br />has disadvantage on all checks and attacks if they
      can see the source of fear, also can not move closer to fear source
    </div>
    <div class="grappled"><b>Grappled</b> <br />stuck in place</div>
    <div class="incapacitated">
      <b>Incapacitated</b><br />
      can't take actions or reactions
    </div>
    <div class="invisibl">
      <b>Invisible</b><br />
      impossible to see without magic aid, considered heavily obscured, can
      still be heard attacks while invisible have advantage and attacks against
      an invisible target have disadvantage
    </div>
    <div class="paralyzed">
      <b>Paralyzed</b><br />
      incapacitated can't move or speak automatically fails STR and DEX saving
      throws attacking paralyzed target have advantage, attack hits are
      automatically CRITS if within 5 feet
    </div>
    <div class="petrified">
      <b>Petrified</b><br />
      creature and NON-magical items it has on person turn to stone, Weight is
      multiplied by 10, stops aging, creature in incapacitated unaware of
      surroundings, attacks against creature have advantage, auto fail STR and
      DEX saving throws, has resistance to all damage (half damage), immune to
      poison, and disease, if already poisoned or diseased they are paused, not
      cured
    </div>
    <div class="poisoned">
      <b>Poisoned</b>
      <br />has disadvantage on attacks and ability checks
    </div>
    <div class="prone">
      <b>Prone</b>
      <br />can only crawl, until standing up, has disadvantage on attacks,
      attacks to prone target with-in 5 ft have advantage, if more than five
      feet away the attacker has disadvantage
    </div>
    <div class="restrained">
      <b>Restrained</b><br />
      speed becomes 0, disadvantage to DEX saving throw, attacks v restrained
      creature have advantage and attacks from the restrained creature have
      disadvantage
    </div>
    <div class="stunned">
      <b>Stunned</b>
      <br />becomes incapacitated, faltered speech, auto fail STR and DEX saving
      throws, attacks against creature have advantage
    </div>
    <div class="unconscious">
      <b>Unconscious</b>
      <br />incapacitated, can't move, speak and is unaware of surroundings,
      immediately drops what ever it is holding and falls prone, auto fail STR
      and DEX saving throw, attack rolls against creature have advantage, if hit
      from creature with in 5 ft it is auto crit
    </div>
  </div>
</div>